data.description: Enjoy living in this PRIME location near Children's Hospital, DIA, Aurora Sports Park and Cherry Creek State Park with plenty of shopping and restaurants at your doorstep! This quiet community boasts large evergreen trees and walking path along the Highline Canal Trail.  Step inside, and you will be met with fresh updates and natural light. This ground level unit has a private patio area connected to an spacious living-dining room with cozy wood burning fireplace and completely remodeled kitchen.  The primary suite boasts a walk-in closet, private bathroom and large walk-in shower with a separate vanity area and sink.  The second bedroom could be transformed into an additional living space or office, and the main bath offers convenience in location for entertaining. In-unit laundry hookups, and a pantry or coat closet complete the functionality of this condo.  Pride of ownership shows throughout, with new floors, granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, new appliances and tile, a brand new shower installed in the primary bathroom, WIFI overhead lighting to connect to your playlist, and new toilets. A secure front entrance, underground parking with reserved space and private storage unit offer some additional perks to this condo. The HOA covers the water, grounds maintenance, pool, and nearby tennis courts. Surrounded by numerous parks, endless entertainment and shopping options. Come see why this could the perfect space to make your own!
